OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has said the UK's
OL,8,F"cast-iron" support of Ukraine will
OL,9,F"always endure", as he made a final
OL,10,Fvisit to the country as Prime Minister.
OL,12,FThe outgoing Labour leader will meet
OL,13,FUkrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky
OL,14,Fduring a high-security trip to the war-
OL,15,Ftorn country's capital Kyiv on
OL,16,FThursday for the last time before
OL,17,Fleaving office.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]qD@AOUqD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
