CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FHe is expected to tell Mr Zelensky
OL,8,Fthat the UK's commitment to backing
OL,9,FUkraine will continue after he is
OL,10,Freplaced by Andy Burnham, who is set
OL,11,Fto be the fifth prime minister since
OL,12,FRussia's invasion of the country in
OL,13,F2022.
OL,15,FMr Burnham will become Labour leader
OL,16,Fon Friday before taking over as prime
OL,17,Fminister on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
