CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FSir Keir said: "Throughout this
OL,8,Fconflict, I have seen the incredible
OL,9,Ffortitude of the Ukrainian people and
OL,10,Fthe iron will of a nation that refuses
OL,11,Fto be cowed.
OL,13,F"Their stand has not only defended its
OL,14,Fown freedom, it has preserved the
OL,15,Fsecurity of Europe.
OL,17,F"When I became Prime Minister, I knew
OL,18,Fthe UK must not simply stand with
OL,19,FUkraine in the moment, but help build
OL,20,Fthe foundations of its long-term
OL,21,Fsecurity and success.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,F"That's why we put the UK at the
OL,8,Fcentre of a stronger Europe `
OL,9,Finvesting more money into defence,
OL,10,Fleading the way in the war fighting
OL,11,Ftechnologies of the future and doing
OL,12,Feverything we can to put Ukraine in
OL,13,Fthe strongest possible position.
OL,15,F"And we have brought others with us on
OL,16,Fthat journey. As we showed at the G7
OL,17,Fand Nato summits, in recent weeks, the
OL,18,FUK and its allies are absolutely
OL,19,Funited against Russian aggression.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,F"I am so proud of what Britain has
OL,8,Fcontributed. That work will continue,
OL,9,Fand our cast-iron support for Ukraine
OL,10,Fwill always endure.
OL,12,F"Not just for them and for European
OL,13,Fsecurity, but for families in Britain
OL,14,Fwho have felt the cost of this war
OL,15,Fthrough rising prices."
OL,17,FSir Keir will also hear how allies can
OL,18,Ffurther meet the needs of Ukraine.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
