OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FThe first of 150 British-made,
OL,8,Fartillery barrels are being provided
OL,9,Fto Ukraine to strengthen their defence
OL,10,Funder a #61 million contract with BAE
OL,11,FSystems.
OL,13,FThe 105mm and 155mm gun barrels are
OL,14,Fbeing produced at Sheffield
OL,15,FForgemasters, the first time forged
OL,16,Fartillery barrels have been produced
OL,17,Fin the UK for almost two decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
