OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister's trip comes days
OL,8,Fafter Ukrainian air defences
OL,9,Fintercepted five ballistic missiles
OL,10,Flaunched by Russia in a raft of night
OL,11,Fattacks, the country's air force said,
OL,12,Fthough other missiles and drones got
OL,13,Fthrough and hit Kyiv.
OL,15,FIn the capital, the attack caused
OL,16,Ffires at two warehouses, while a
OL,17,Fschool was also damaged, the city's
OL,18,Fmayor Vitali Klitschko said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FThe Russian Defence Ministry said in a
OL,8,Fstatement that the attack targeted
OL,9,Fmilitary manufacturing facilities in
OL,10,Fthe Ukrainian capital that produce
OL,11,Flong-range missiles and drones.
OL,13,FUkraine's air force said one ballistic
OL,14,Fmissile and 25 drones struck 17
OL,15,Flocations, while falling debris was
OL,16,Freported in 10 locations.
OL,18,FThe Prime Minister is spending his
OL,19,Ffinal days in office highlighting what
OL,20,Fhe sees as his legacy, including
OL,21,Fsupport for Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
