OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FHe began the week in Paris where he
OL,8,Fattended a meeting of the "coalition
OL,9,Fof the willing" group.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday morning, he was with
OL,12,FEmmanuel Macron and other leaders at
OL,13,Fthe Bastille Day celebrations in the
OL,14,FFrench capital in a sign of the closer
OL,15,Frelationship he has tried to forge
OL,16,Fwith European neighbours as part of
OL,17,Fhis post-Brexit reset.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
