OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FMr Macron awarded Sir Keir the Legion
OL,8,Fd'honneur in recognition of his
OL,9,Fsupport for Ukraine and European
OL,10,Frelations.
OL,12,FSir Keir's time as Prime Minister has
OL,13,Fseen the signing of a 100-year
OL,14,Fpartnership between the UK and
OL,15,FUkraine, aimed at fostering closer
OL,16,Fdefence and trade ties among other
OL,17,Fthings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FAfter a tempestuous exchange with
OL,8,FDonald Trump in the White House last
OL,9,Fyear, Mr Zelensky was invited to
OL,10,FLondon for a summit at Lancaster House.
OL,12,FSir Keir led efforts during the
OL,13,Fgathering of mainly European leaders
OL,14,Fto establish a peacekeeping force
OL,15,Faimed at deterring Russia in the event
OL,16,Fof an end to the war.
OL,18,FEarlier this week, it was also
OL,19,Fannounced that Britain is joining the
OL,20,FEU's 90 billion euro (#78 billion)
OL,21,Floan to Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784184477
OL,3,CKeir Starmer says UK support for
OL,4,CUkraine will 'always endure' on
OL,5,Cfarewell visit
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister said British firms
OL,8,Fwould be able to bid for contracts
OL,9,Ffunded by the EU's Ukraine support
OL,10,Floan.
OL,12,FThe loan is intended to help cover
OL,13,FKyiv's most urgent defence and
OL,14,Fbudgetary needs in 2026 and 2027, with
OL,15,Ftwo-thirds of the total allocated to
OL,16,Fmilitary spending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
